Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个岛上的男人们每年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都会举办只有男人参加的大船捕鱼大会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在12年前的大会时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.63,0:00:31.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现了百年难见的大浪袭击了小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人们都被漂流到了岛屿之外…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是这个岛上没有一个男人的缘由？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.00,0:00:43.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对  不过只是从婆婆那里听来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说  那大浪再来的话就能出岛了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.74,0:00:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但婆婆说那是百年难得一见的大浪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.94,0:00:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算来的时候  下次也会在…嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.40,0:01:00.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,107年后？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…我觉得你这计算错了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.55,0:01:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗  奇怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.31,0:01:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算如此等下去  也会变成爷爷了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:13.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.07,0:01:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之  今天发生了许多  行人也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡…睡是…在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:23.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人可以先睡的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.28,0:01:25.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去洗下澡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:03.01,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被围追的  女婿殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:08.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以后会变成怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.46,0:03:11.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于离开父亲  获得自由了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然从父亲那里获得了自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.69,0:03:24.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请自由的对待我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:26.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:27.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:27.97,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.17,0:03:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.01,0:03:30.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:33.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅自在别人家做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得让行人住在这样破旧狭窄肮脏的房间里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,度过蓝兰岛的第一个夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.23,0:03:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.29,0:03:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃  别管这些  快点穿衣服  衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:48.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不得不和你做个决断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论试几次做结果都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决断什么的就算了  铃  快穿衣服  衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.14,0:04:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.37,0:04:11.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  为什么会把这说成是别人的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多说无益！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:16.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.39,0:04:31.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说了  快穿衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.20,0:04:35.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.47,0:04:45.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:46.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  都怎么了  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:58.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡十二年的女人本能觉醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.35,0:05:00.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点担心过来看看居然是这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样的话就只能用「那个」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.45,0:05:05.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.22,0:05:08.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静～！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.78,0:05:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好好听着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:13.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚这男人由我保管
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抉择是在明天
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.26,0:05:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用争夺女婿殿下捉迷藏大会决出胜负～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.33,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竖日早上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.81,0:05:30.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我不得不成为女婿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.46,0:05:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人一个都没有  现在要灭亡之时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你漂流到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:40.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这已经是天命了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.61,0:05:44.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么年轻就结婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:47.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十四  十五岁结婚是很正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以前的事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.38,0:05:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管以前还是现在都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:54.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相爱的人能在一起就是幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和年龄没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.68,0:06:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不在这里决定你属于谁的话  就停止不了骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我又不是东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.17,0:06:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,互相成为对方的东西  结婚不就是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要这样的婚姻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.37,0:06:12.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只会说那种伟大的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:17.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样不单是一个  全部都成为新娘的话怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.00,0:06:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样人口也会增加  正好得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:25.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样你就会很辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我接受  我接受了就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.93,0:06:30.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.80,0:06:33.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样只有堂堂正正的甩掉她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:39.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样应该谁都不用选了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:45.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争夺女婿大人的躲藏大会开幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,规则有三条
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.12,0:06:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  范围只是岛的西边  特别是东边的森林不能进
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.40,0:06:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二  时限到夕阳沉入水平线
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:07:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三  最先碰到女婿殿下的人是胜者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.42,0:07:11.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样  对体力还是有自信的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.32,0:07:18.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以女人的脚力能追上我吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.11,0:07:18.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.16,0:07:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说好恐怖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.63,0:07:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  这样下去会被追上的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:24.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,炸猪排？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:38.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道发生什么  趁现在快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.19,0:07:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.51,0:07:45.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:49.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜错了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子决出胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.10,0:07:56.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:58.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别和她有关系才是上策
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.38,0:07:59.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.51,0:08:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  行人殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.09,0:08:02.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.50,0:08:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算甩开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去绝对能逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.80,0:08:15.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.09,0:08:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西的话要到高处最好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.48,0:08:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说登高的本领  我是最厉害的！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做的这些事情真是失败
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也做了那么美妙的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:34.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:42.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天虽然有点大意  今天没那…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.54,0:08:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在很急
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是怎么回事——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.92,0:08:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  新娘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是很憧憬的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.49,0:09:06.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且结婚的话  那些缠我的家伙也会消失啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.18,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（很受同性欢迎的类型）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:11.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这场胜负  我赢定了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.30,0:09:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉到了什么气息…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.61,0:09:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是错觉吗…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.75,0:09:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:31.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.29,0:09:32.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  请别逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把你藏到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.35,0:09:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对结婚没有兴趣  请安心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:43.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗  真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.24,0:09:45.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:51.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相对地  对男性这种生物却有很深的兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.61,0:09:57.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…难道是陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.25,0:10:08.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀  那边有连这岛上最博学的我都没看见过的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.86,0:10:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带有传说气息的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.99,0:10:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会让身体变大的蘑菇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.64,0:10:19.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人就成为我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:25.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我从每寸肌肤和那个身体生态研究吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.81,0:10:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没事吧  千影小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.26,0:10:34.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}（自作自受）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.55,0:10:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.70,0:10:38.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到  发现
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.27,0:10:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是缠人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.84,0:10:52.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来为什么会有这种体力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:55.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且为什么每天不得不遭遇这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.99,0:10:59.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会放弃  难得脱离父亲得到的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.01,0:11:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:04.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.80,0:11:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.22,0:11:16.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然遇上了一条河啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:22.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.09,0:11:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫町
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:33.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小女子不才  请指教
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:37.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快  请
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶  就这样输的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好抓住  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.97,0:11:47.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.39,0:11:53.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要…决断…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  现在不是做这个的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:11:59.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.69,0:12:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么能这样输了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:31.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  这样的河应该会…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:49.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰鹰？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.26,0:12:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  铃姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有这个不会让给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:13:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纹次郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.70,0:13:06.41,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}（鸵鸟  不会飞）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这笨鸟  那么华丽的登场之后居然是这副蠢样子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.67,0:13:07.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想点什么办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.22,0:13:12.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能得到女婿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.39,0:13:16.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪乃就能作为出色的大人  被大家承认了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我应该掉下瀑布悬崖了的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…在飞！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放我下来  放我下来  我在高处是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:27.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  别乱动  别乱动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.12,0:13:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真的放我下来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  行人？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  那里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  糟糕了  到东边的森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.76,0:14:04.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  是风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:08.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  这里是哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很不好的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃跑比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.93,0:14:30.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  行人和炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东边的森林是全是食肉植物的危险地带
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:40.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:46.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是什么岛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.85,0:14:56.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那里有比食肉植物更加可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东边森林之主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.41,0:15:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在行人被发现之前  不救出来的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.14,0:15:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回  又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:20.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我以后会小心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.37,0:15:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊  我还在想会是什么怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.93,0:15:30.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是可爱的熊猫吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.82,0:15:45.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难…难道是说  生气了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.10,0:15:59.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.92,0:16:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.36,0:16:03.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.68,0:16:08.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记了  现在正在捉迷藏中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:11.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃也参加大赛的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.92,0:16:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不会想让我成为女婿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:18.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然救我很感谢  但是不逃离这里的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.80,0:16:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.03,0:16:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.09,0:16:36.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹰鹰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.22,0:16:39.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西边的悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.17,0:16:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在西边的悬崖
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.71,0:16:43.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.85,0:16:46.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今日一定要做决断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:51.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:57.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,争夺女婿捉迷藏大会…？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人殿下…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.19,0:17:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夕…夕阳还没沉吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:24.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然很想睡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.00,0:17:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:35.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体…麻痹了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:41.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  炸猪排
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.06,0:17:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.95,0:17:46.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没碰他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.03,0:17:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明摆着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.27,0:17:57.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在不甘心的铃面前抓住的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.11,0:18:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会很爽啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.45,0:18:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,射中了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:17.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐大人特制的麻痹药怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是你也不能动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看样子决出胜负了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要这样对铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.96,0:18:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.42,0:18:33.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从以前开始铃在什么大会都是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与此相比我每次都最后
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.58,0:18:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是十分火大！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是在妨碍别人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:44.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是最火大的是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.19,0:18:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.83,0:18:50.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明前一阵子里还和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么短时间内就超越我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.17,0:18:54.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还是压倒性的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是我喜欢就让它变大的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.35,0:18:59.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…就是理由？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.99,0:19:05.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是用今天的胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.17,0:19:09.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能勾销至今的全部失败
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.41,0:19:10.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个岛唯一的男人成为我的仆人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.74,0:19:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反抗是不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:31.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖的成为我的东西吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.29,0:19:32.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:36.24,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（真人）
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  夕阳沉下了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.50,0:19:56.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:57.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:19:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.98,0:20:04.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么是我输了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有好好的逃走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.00,0:20:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没  我一直都监视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.37,0:20:13.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优胜者是——
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…铃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.39,0:20:20.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么时候被铃抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.17,0:20:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没说一定要抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.69,0:20:25.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是碰到的就是赢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.77,0:20:29.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险…险…险…险…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.31,0:20:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候确实你摸到铃了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.32,0:20:34.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（摸到那里了吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.53,0:20:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  东边的森林是范围以外  应该不算…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.89,0:20:37.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.70,0:20:40.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:42.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多小孩就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.98,0:20:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.34,0:20:46.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情还是无法接受…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.34,0:20:46.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…对行人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.08,0:20:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:02.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.31,0:21:03.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.93,0:21:05.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样很奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:06.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆不是说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚是要和喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以行人和谁结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.33,0:21:14.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要等到行人的喜欢的人出现
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.14,0:21:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那个人相爱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢的等着  有什么不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.62,0:21:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  大家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.61,0:21:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.93,0:21:22.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.20,0:21:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢  这样也好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么做  反正一生都离不开这座岛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.73,0:21:29.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:31.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  行人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.35,0:21:34.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗…算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.14,0:21:36.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.22,0:21:36.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:40.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  铃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行人  为了增加友谊来我家吃饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.01,0:21:46.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.01,0:21:47.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来我家吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.09,0:21:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是什么都没有解决吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.51,0:21:54.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:29.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我赢了  铃…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.29,0:23:33.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)}来吧来吧  行人  今天开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.39,0:23:20.08,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\3c&HE7A573}「有用的住宿者」
